.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣都唔可以停<br />\n要keep 住個氣氛直到G20<br />\n到時林奠兩面不是人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外留林奠有用，上次幫完English Tsoi 助攻<br />\n下次到民賤聯同工賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb6ab20994403eefe6a2045b5c56f3ac335d136","tid":1241311,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"救埋人先係最好結果"},{"pid":"61820a4b221dc849eafafd316c5c16fc6f7714da","tid":1241311,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb6ab20994403eefe6a2045b5c56f3ac335d136","tid":1241311,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"救埋人先係最好結果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但呢方面真係要大狀幫手<br />\n<br />\n上次個反送中被捕人支援基金仲係唔係運作緊？"},{"pid":"8793bb3e9016b197b6ed1a7d2ad27b195a3c0bc1","tid":1241311,"uid":38780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"家陣明顯就係政府想拖<br />\n佢5個訴求一個都無做到<br />\n點樣叫好？？？<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人係唔會接受咁既道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4701555513d02bd6db3999acee4c2a580a7f00c5","tid":1241311,"uid":25477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"人就一定要救既，老老實實佢今日對記者既態度已經好佐好多，無以前串柒柒，好記得以前中文答撚完英文唔答。 而家我覺得要做係迫佢成立委員會去調查班犬。一定要警察認錯，同埋點撚樣可以令柒婆保持住呢一個無咁臭串高高在上既態度。利申唔係鬼。都想大家團結叫警察認錯，同埋唔會拉到學生"},{"pid":"9133072d7a06806baafe24fdf09f3ce28f8e3ccb","tid":1241311,"uid":179409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"大家都想贏<br />\n問題係依家呢個贏真係假像嚟<br />\n就算當送中暫緩係等於停咗<br />\n但至少要等到出年立法會換屆先算真係安心<br />\n如果唔係一陣佢連續推幾條有爭議嘅議案<br />\n當中夾雜返送中二讀就仆街<br />\n呢個政府太卑鄙無恥<br />\n無咩做唔出<br />\n而且暴動呢個定性一日唔徹回<br />\n好多無辜嘅人都有機會俾政府誣告<br />\n仲有<br />\n一定要追究下令開槍嘅指揮官<br />\n至少告得入一兩個做警示<br />\n革職也好、坐監也好<br />\n先會令黑警日後唔敢再發神經攻擊市民<br />\n一日唔徹回暴動定性同追究到邊個渣警下令開槍<br />\n都唔算係贏<br />\n呢兩個我覺得已經係最低要求"},{"pid":"67420ebb414396523416a97b14c5511654d04d5c","tid":1241311,"uid":155107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8793bb3e9016b197b6ed1a7d2ad27b195a3c0bc1","tid":1241311,"uid":38780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"家陣明顯就係政府想拖<br />\n佢5個訴求一個都無做到<br />\n點樣叫好？？？<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人係唔會接受咁既道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"有良知既人，嬲係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我地係務實既，最緊要救義士<br />\n<br />\n同追究狗隻<br />\n<br />\n要留返有用之軀"},{"pid":"2662ba45896d706a16422d59b882c8f70b00aa4d","tid":1241311,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61820a4b221dc849eafafd316c5c16fc6f7714da","tid":1241311,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb6ab20994403eefe6a2045b5c56f3ac335d136","tid":1241311,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"救埋人先係最好結果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但呢方面真係要大狀幫手<br />\n<br />\n上次個反送中被捕人支援基金仲係唔係運作緊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"有冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683400c74ef990fd90e439ab760ada31e61a5521","tid":1241311,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:31:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"000ccf3ddb7be2f74f5f